00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:41,520
Yeah. Has it made you feel better?

633
00:39:43,080 --> 00:39:44,800
I think it has.

634
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:49,120
It's made me feel like
there's some good in the world

635
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:51,480
