00:41:53,160 --> 00:41:55,640
and I'm holding onto you
as tight as I can.

676
00:41:57,680 --> 00:41:59,440
And then what happens?

677
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:02,040
Nothing.

678
00:42:02,080 --> 00:42:04,840
Just ride, Chris. Just ride.

679
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:10,440
Well...

